Class SCUIGUIDataContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.context.SCUIGUIDataContext

  • public class SCUIGUIDataContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class which holds the GUI related data.
    For example this object can potentially hold the output of all struts action calls and other metadata which is required for the presentation layer. statikonda
